text: Dumitru Sulică (16 April 1921 - 1987) was a Romanian alpine skier. He competed at the 1948 Winter Olympics and the 1952 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:1987 deaths Category:Romanian male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Romania Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:Alpine skiers at the 1952 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Brașov
